WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.408 --> 00:00:01.835
How does logistics meet the needs

2
00:00:01.835 --> 00:00:04.336
of the business to help Veterans?

3
00:00:04.336 --> 00:00:06.952
First by responsible purchasing.

4
00:00:06.952 --> 00:00:09.081
Ensure that you buy the right product

5
00:00:09.081 --> 00:00:11.199
at the right time in the right amount

6
00:00:11.199 --> 00:00:12.860
to support treatment for Veterans

7
00:00:12.860 --> 00:00:14.313
and their families.

8
00:00:14.313 --> 00:00:16.016
Manage stock appropriately

9
00:00:16.016 --> 00:00:19.239
to ensure storage under appropriate conditions.

10
00:00:19.239 --> 00:00:21.652
Rotate stock to eliminate expiration

11
00:00:21.652 --> 00:00:23.611
and misuse of products,

12
00:00:23.611 --> 00:00:26.104
and manage recalls and pull affected product

13
00:00:26.104 --> 00:00:27.851
without interrupting patient care.

